  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Hestan vs Thermador — both LA-local parts advantage</h2>
    <p>Hestan and Thermador are the two luxury residential stove brands with LA-local parts advantage. Anaheim (Hestan) and Irvine (Thermador BSH warehouse) are both inside 1-3 day parts delivery for LA authorized service.</p>
    <p><b>Hestan (this page)</b> — Meyer Corp Anaheim factory 2014+, sealed-burner Pro Series, Hestan Cue smart integration, Bordeaux + Matte color program, newer luxury-category entrant. Parts 1-3 day from Anaheim.</p>
    <p><b>Thermador</b> — BSH Hausgeräte Irvine parts warehouse, Star Burner + ExtraLow pulse-cycle simmer signature, Pro Grand 36/48/60 + Pro Grand Steam, broader installed base since 1916 LA founding. Parts 1-2 day from Irvine. See <a href="/brands/thermador-stove-repair/">Thermador stove repair</a>.</p>
    <p>Choice drivers: Hestan for Cue smart + newer engineering + Bordeaux / Matte color; Thermador for BSH heritage + ExtraLow simmer precision + broader parts network + Pro Grand Steam oven-chamber feature. Both LA-local parts-proximate.</p>
